This is the README file for CPANPLUS::Daemon

Please refer to 'perldoc CPANPLUS::Daemon' after installation for
details.

#####################################################################

* Description

CPANPLUS::Daemon

    CPANPLUS::Daemon let's you run a daemon that listens on a
    specified port and can act as a remote backend to your
    CPANPLUS::Shell::Default

#####################################################################

* Installation

CPANPLUS::Daemon follows the standard perl module install process

perl Makefile.PL
make
make test
make install

The module uses no C or XS parts, so no c-compiler is required.

